data.description: SO MUCH Larger than it appears! Opportunity is knocking with a chance to own and customize this Turn-of-the-Century classic in a great neighborhood near the center of town and legendary Coopers Pond.  The home features 5 beds and 2.5 baths on 4 levels.  Hardwood floors on 1st/2nd.  Approx 2100 SF per tax records.  Oversize detached garage with loft storage. Patio for entertaining. Convenient to houses of worship, schools, shopping, dining, parks, and NYC transportation.
